{"title":"照“顾”之“客”","authors":["冯德芳"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":2,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"照“顾”之“客”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冯德芳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最近，笔者在柳州市某肉店听到一段对话，笔录下来，以新读者耳目："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拄杖老者：“同志，我买排骨。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年青女营业员：“没有了。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“肉案下不是还有好多吗？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“那是顾客的。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我不也是顾客吗？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“那是照‘顾’之‘客’的。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“噢！原来如此！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}